v2.0.3

New: Now, in the order form for desktop, when double clicking ticket text box, it's zoomed-in within 
	a modal window.
	
New: In an order's dash board (form), items ordered by a user other than the current logged user are colored
	with a color identifying the creating user. For the case of additions, the creating user is identified by
	its login name.

New: A full cleaning feature of system state (business data and history) is added. Besides business 
	configuration, the only data kept is the quantity and value of items stored in warehouses, 
	cash register balances, and customers. 

